		<div id="contactteam">
			
			<div id="seeForms">
				<div>
					<img style="aspect-ratio: 2 / 1" src="Images/strobinglights.jpg" alt="Picture of strobing lights">
					<div>
						<h2>BOOK STAGE FRIGHT</h2>
						<div>
							<p>Planning an event and want an electrifying performance? Fill out the form to request Stage Fright for your concert, festival, or corporate event. Provide as much detail as possible, and our team will get back to you within 3-5 business days to confirm availability and discuss logistics.</p>
							<button onclick="showForm('booking')">SHOW FORM</button>
						</div>
					</div>    
				</div>
				<div>
					<div>
						<h2>CUSTOMER SERVICE</h2>
						<div>
							<p>Have a question or issue with tickets, merch, or an event? Submit the form, and our support team will get back to you within 24-48 hours. Be sure to include your order number if applicable for faster service. Check your email for a response!</p>
							<button onclick="showForm('customers')">SHOW FORM</button>
						</div>
					</div>
					<img style="aspect-ratio: 2 / 1" src="Images/microphone.jpg" alt="Picture of microphone">
				</div>
				<div>
					<img style="aspect-ratio: 2 / 1; transform: scaleX(-1)" src="Images/strobinglights.jpg" alt="Picture of strobing lights">
					<div>
						<h2>GENERAL INQUIRIES</h2>
						<div>
							<p>Curious about the band, media requests, or partnership opportunities? Complete this form and share your message. Expect a response in 3-5 business days. Keep an eye on your inbox, and don’t forget to check your spam folder just in case!</p>
							<button onclick="showForm('emailgen')">SHOW FORM</button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div>
					<div>
						<h2>JOIN THE MAILING LIST</h2>
						<div>
							<p>Stay in the loop and never miss an update! Sign up to receive the latest news, exclusive offers, and important announcements straight to your inbox. We’ll keep you informed on everything related to Stage Fright, from upcoming events to new releases and promotions.</p>
							<button onclick="showForm('signup')">SHOW FORM</button>
						</div>
					</div>   
					<img style="aspect-ratio: 2 / 1" src="Images/blurrycrowd.jpg" alt="Picture of blurry crowd in blue light">					
				</div>
			</div>

			<div id="booking" class="form-popup">
				<form>
					<button class="close-btn" onclick="closeForm('booking')">X</button>				
					<h2>Book Stage Fright</h2>
					<div class="form-section-container">
						<div class="form-section">
							<label for="event-name">Event Name/Type:</label>
							<input type="text" id="event-name" name="event-name" placeholder="e.g. Summer Music Festival" required>

							<label for="event-date">Event Date:</label>
							<input type="date" id="event-date" name="event-date" required>

							<label for="event-time">Event Time:</label>
							<input type="time" id="event-time" name="event-time" required>

							<label for="venue-location">Venue Location:</label>
							<input type="text" id="venue-location" name="venue-location" placeholder="e.g. Doe Arena 281 First St." required>
						</div>

						<div class="form-section">
							<label for="contact-name">Your Name:</label>
							<input type="text" id="contact-name" name="contact-name" placeholder="e.g. John Doe" required>

							<label for="user-position">Your Position:</label>
							<input type="text" id="user-position" name="user-position" placeholder="e.g. Executive Supervisor" required>

							<label for="contact-email">Email:</label>
							<input type="email" id="contact-email" name="contact-email" placeholder="e.g. youremail@gmail.com" required>

							<label for="pnumber2">Phone Number:</label>
							<input type="tel" id="pnumber2" name="contact-phone" placeholder="e.g. (123) 456-7890" required>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="form-section-long">
						<label for="additional-notes">Additional Notes:</label>
						<textarea id="additional-notes" name="additional-notes" placeholder="e.g. Special conditions, Rain dates, etc." rows="4"></textarea>
					</div>

					<button type="submit">Send Booking Request</button>
				</form>
			</div>

			<div id="customers" class="form-popup">			
				<form>
				<button class="close-btn" onclick="closeForm('customers')">X</button>
					<h2>Customer Service</h2>
					<div class="form-section-container">
						<div class="form-section">
							<label for="name">Your Name:</label>
							<input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="e.g. John Doe" required>

							<label for="email">Email:</label>
							<input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="e.g. youremail@gmail.com" required>

							<label for="phone">Phone Number:</label>
							<input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="e.g. (123) 456-7890" required>
						</div>

						<div class="form-section">
							<label for="order-number">Order Number (if applicable):</label>
							<input type="text" id="order-number" name="order-number" placeholder="e.g. Order 12345678">

							<label for="purchase-date">Date of Purchase (if applicable):</label>
							<input type="date" id="purchase-date" name="purchase-date">
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="form-section-long">
						<label for="issue-description">Description of Issue:</label>
						<textarea id="issue-description" name="issue-description" placeholder="e.g. Issue with product, Issue at event, etc." rows="4" required></textarea> 
					</div>

					<button type="submit">Submit</button>
				</form>
			</div>

			<div id="emailgen" class="form-popup">
				<form>
				<button class="close-btn" onclick="closeForm('emailgen')">X</button>
					<h2>General Inquiries</h2>
					<div class="form-section-container">
						<div class="form-section">
							<label for="name2">Your Name:</label>
							<input type="text" id="name2" name="name" placeholder="e.g. John Doe" required>

							<label for="email2">Email:</label>
							<input type="email" id="email2" name="email" placeholder="e.g. youremail@gmail.com" required>

							<label for="subject">Subject:</label>
							<input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" placeholder="e.g. Questions about touring, recording, etc.">

							<label for="message">Message:</label>
							<textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="e.g. What media is my company legally allowed to use for commercial purposes?" rows="4" required></textarea>
						</div>
					</div>
					<button type="submit">Submit Inquiry</button>
				</form>
			</div>
			
			<div id="signup" class="form-popup">			
				<form>
					<button class="close-btn" onclick="closeForm('signup')">X</button>
					<h2>Join the Mailing List</h2>
					<label for="name3">Full Name:</label>
					<input type="text" id="name3" name="name" placeholder="e.g. John Doe" required>

					<label for="email3">Your Email:</label>
					<input type="email" id="email3" name="email" placeholder="e.g. youremail@gmail.com" required>

					<label for="pnumber">Phone Number:</label>
					<input type="text" id="pnumber" name="pnumber" placeholder="e.g. (XXX) XXX-XXXX" maxlength="14" required>
					
					<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; margin: 10px 0;">
						<input type="checkbox" id="sms_opt_in" name="sms_opt_in" value="yes">
						<label for="sms_opt_in">
							I would like to receive text messages about updates, promotions, and reminders.
						</label>
					</div>
					
					<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; margin: 10px 0;">
						<input type="checkbox" id="terms_agreement" name="terms_agreement" value="yes" required>
						<label for="agree_terms">
							I confirm that the information provided is accurate, and I agree to receive communications as per the organization's policies.
						</label>
					</div>

					<button type="submit">Sign Up</button>
				</form>
			</div>

			<div class="footer-img" style="background-position: bottom; background-image: url('Images/HEADINGS/cymbal.jpg')"></div>
		</div>	
	</body>
